<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 06:08:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在东耶路撒冷被以色列警察枪杀的巴勒斯坦男孩的家人表示他没有构成危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/family-of-palestinian-boy-shot-dead-by-police-in-east-jerusalem-say-he-posed-no-danger/0000018e-390b-dc74-adbe-bdaf41ef0000</link><description>一段视频显示，12 岁的拉米·哈姆丹 (Rami Hamdan) 站在另一个男孩旁边，两人都拿着绑在棍子上的鞭炮。在鞭炮放响之前，听到一声枪响，他摔倒了。 “警察在厚厚的混凝土后面。即使它击中了他们，他们也不会发生任何事情，”他的父亲说</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 04:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/family-of-palestinian-boy-shot-dead-by-police-in-east-jerusalem-say-he-posed-no-danger/0000018e-390b-dc74-adbe-bdaf41ef0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的分配困境：随着饥饿蔓延，捐助者寻求私营公司来处理援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-distribution-dilemma-as-hunger-spreads-donors-seek-private-firms-to-handle-aid/0000018e-39fd-d3fc-adff-b9ff1f180000</link><description>第一批海上援助物资——200吨食品和药品——已离开塞浦路斯前往加沙地带，但后勤困难将使这一过程变得复杂，美国政府没有解决方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 04:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-distribution-dilemma-as-hunger-spreads-donors-seek-private-firms-to-handle-aid/0000018e-39fd-d3fc-adff-b9ff1f180000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙封锁特拉维夫主要高速公路上扣押的以色列人质的亲属</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article-live/report-u-s-would-back-israeli-op-against-hamas-leaders-in-rafah-if-idf-does-not-invade/0000018e-3aad-d823-adaf-7baf11d50000</link><description>报告：美国预计将对被占领的约旦河西岸以色列前哨基地实施新制裁 ■ 勇敢暗示拉法在加沙的行动 ■ 真主党主席：以色列与哈马斯的谈判是“失败”的迹象 ■ 报告：美国与伊朗举行秘密谈判以阻止胡塞武装袭击■ 以色列表示改变加沙援助政策，打算向加沙“淹没”援助 ■ 据报道，以色列袭击拉法食品配送中心后，至少一名近东救济工程处工作人员死亡，22 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article-live/report-u-s-would-back-israeli-op-against-hamas-leaders-in-rafah-if-idf-does-not-invade/0000018e-3aad-d823-adaf-7baf11d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将废除“多余”的情报部，略微精简臃肿的政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-scrap-superfluous-intelligence-ministry-slightly-slimming-bloated-government/0000018e-3999-d2fd-a1fe-3df9ac7a0000</link><description>现任部长吉拉·加姆利尔(Gila Gamliel)将接任科学部长，接替奥菲尔·阿库尼斯(Ofir Akunis)，奥菲尔·阿库尼斯将前往纽约担任以色列总领事</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:16:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-scrap-superfluous-intelligence-ministry-slightly-slimming-bloated-government/0000018e-3999-d2fd-a1fe-3df9ac7a0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学100名教员反对对指控以色列种族灭绝的学者进行停职，质疑哈马斯暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/100-hebrew-university-faculty-protest-suspension-of-scholar-alleging-israeli-gaza-genocide/0000018e-3993-d3fc-adff-b9b383330000</link><description>现任和前任教职员工写道，尽管他们反对沙尔赫布-凯沃基安的观点，但管理层无权让她停职。他们补充说，此举可能会增加国际学术抵制该大学的呼声</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/100-hebrew-university-faculty-protest-suspension-of-scholar-alleging-israeli-gaza-genocide/0000018e-3993-d3fc-adff-b9b383330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学是否应该解雇一名称哈马斯暴行是“谎言”的学者？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-13/ty-article/.highlight/should-an-israeli-university-fire-an-academic-who-said-hamas-atrocities-are-lies/0000018e-38e7-d21d-a3ef-3be7aa4f0000</link><description>在这一点上，如果所有这些受惊的大学管理部门和愤怒的抵制者都得逞，校园里唯一剩下的争论将是关于自助餐厅的选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:13:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-13/ty-article/.highlight/should-an-israeli-university-fire-an-academic-who-said-hamas-atrocities-are-lies/0000018e-38e7-d21d-a3ef-3be7aa4f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府科学战的另一个目标：享誉世界的火山研究所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/another-target-of-the-israeli-governments-war-on-science-the-acclaimed-volcani-institute/0000018e-3884-d2fd-a1fe-3df56d6d0000</link><description>以色列的粮食安全取决于火山研究所在农业领域所做的开创性工作。预算削减表明以色列政府优先考虑投资过去，而不是未来</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 20:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/another-target-of-the-israeli-governments-war-on-science-the-acclaimed-volcani-institute/0000018e-3884-d2fd-a1fe-3df56d6d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡没有告诉拜登有关以色列人和加沙战争的全部真相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-tell-biden-the-whole-truth-about-israelis-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-389b-dc74-adbe-bcbf118b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡告诉拜登和 AIPAC，以色列人绝大多数支持他的战时政策，而忽略了公众对他的领导力和加沙“全面胜利”承诺的信心下降。问题是以色列人何时以及是否会开始呼吁结束战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-tell-biden-the-whole-truth-about-israelis-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-389b-dc74-adbe-bcbf118b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军最高指挥官在呼吁以色列领导人“无愧于他们的士兵”后接受质询</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</link><description>双桅船。丹·戈德福斯将军呼吁以色列领导人“无愧于预备役军人，他们不关心自己来自哪一方，并肩作战”，并“确保每个人都参与其中”，但这一呼吁并未得到他的上级指挥官的批准。他向加沙地带以外的媒体发表的声明</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</guid></item><item><title>戏剧性的转变，以色列表示打算向加沙“淹没”人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-changes-its-policy-on-supplies-to-gaza-intends-to-flood-in-aid-idf-says/0000018e-390e-db12-a9ef-fbff14c50000</link><description>这一决定是在国际社会向内塔尼亚胡政府施加巨大压力之后做出的，包括在华盛顿和伦敦对来访的部长本尼·甘茨提出严厉警告，甘茨被告知以色列需要采取更多措施来缓解加沙地带的饥饿</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:42:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-changes-its-policy-on-supplies-to-gaza-intends-to-flood-in-aid-idf-says/0000018e-390e-db12-a9ef-fbff14c50000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 159 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-159/0000018e-38e1-d21d-a3ef-3be787fe0000</link><description>南非表示，持有南非公民身份的以色列国防军士兵在进入该国时将被逮捕 ■ 在与拜登之间前所未有的紧张局势中，内塔尼亚胡预计将在参议院共和党撤退问题上发表讲话 ■ 近东救济工程处：据报道，以色列袭击拉法食品配送中心后，至少一名工作人员被杀 ■ 这是自以来的首次10 月 7 日，运载援助物资的卡车直接从以色列进入加沙北部 ■ 战争开始 159 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:39:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-159/0000018e-38e1-d21d-a3ef-3be787fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列一直将约旦河西岸与加沙地带分开。战争期间就等于死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-been-separating-the-west-bank-from-gaza-during-war-it-becomes-a-death-sentence/0000018e-3874-d2fd-a1fe-3df58c940000</link><description>自上世纪90年代以来，以色列一直致力于将巴勒斯坦领土分为两部分。事实上，加沙人暂时流离失所到西岸并未被考虑，这表明以色列造成的分裂是多么根深蒂固。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:23:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-been-separating-the-west-bank-from-gaza-during-war-it-becomes-a-death-sentence/0000018e-3874-d2fd-a1fe-3df58c940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会批准以色列修订后的2024年预算，为加沙战争提供资金，解决联盟争端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/knesset-approves-israels-amended-2024-budget-to-fund-gaza-war-amid-coalition-dispute/0000018e-3863-dda5-a9ff-fdefb3cc0000</link><description>在与战争无关的支出问题上出现政治争端和分歧后，2024 年修订预算法以 62 名支持者对 55 名反对者的多数票获得通过</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:22:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/knesset-approves-israels-amended-2024-budget-to-fund-gaza-war-amid-coalition-dispute/0000018e-3863-dda5-a9ff-fdefb3cc0000</guid></item><item><title>与甘茨分手后，萨尔可能获得战时内阁席位——但内塔尼亚胡担心本-格维尔的要求也会随之而来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/saar-could-get-a-war-cabinet-seat-but-netanyahu-fears-ben-gvirs-demands-will-follow/0000018e-3801-d21d-a3ef-3b4721070000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡并不急于屈服于萨尔的要求，而甘茨的人民坚持认为战时内阁中唯一的空闲席位是为亚伊尔·拉皮德保留的</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/saar-could-get-a-war-cabinet-seat-but-netanyahu-fears-ben-gvirs-demands-will-follow/0000018e-3801-d21d-a3ef-3b4721070000</guid></item><item><title>病毒式斋月广告聚焦以色列加沙战争中的巴勒斯坦儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/the-viral-ramadan-commercial-spotlighting-palestinian-children-amid-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-3389-d9f7-a5ee-f7cbd44a0000</link><description>科威特电信巨头 Zain 今年发布的这段视频突显了加沙灾难性的人道主义局势，以 10 岁难民汉达拉的标志性巴勒斯坦漫画为特色，传达了坚持和回归的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/the-viral-ramadan-commercial-spotlighting-palestinian-children-amid-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-3389-d9f7-a5ee-f7cbd44a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、萨达姆和普京的朋友乔治·加洛韦是英国政治的未来吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/is-george-galloway-friend-of-hamas-saddam-and-putin-the-future-of-british-politics/0000018e-37dd-d2aa-a5ae-f7fdd0290000</link><description>乔治·加洛韦是表演政治的孔雀，现在正处于极左转变为极右的特殊政治暮色中。但他最近在英国选举中取得的成功，被称为“对加沙的公投”和“工人而不是工人”的公投，将进一步推动整个政治领域将战争工具化的热潮</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:24:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/is-george-galloway-friend-of-hamas-saddam-and-putin-the-future-of-british-politics/0000018e-37dd-d2aa-a5ae-f7fdd0290000</guid></item><item><title>富兰克林·福尔：“美国犹太人的日常生活将被反犹太主义打断”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-13/ty-article-podcast/franklin-foer-everyday-jewish-u-s-life-will-be-punctuated-by-antisemitism/0000018e-3535-da0e-a78f-fd3d5cd90000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 13:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-13/ty-article-podcast/franklin-foer-everyday-jewish-u-s-life-will-be-punctuated-by-antisemitism/0000018e-3535-da0e-a78f-fd3d5cd90000</guid></item><item><title>抛弃甘茨后，萨尔并没有给内塔尼亚胡提供救生索。他递给他一个氧气瓶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/by-leaving-gantz-saar-didnt-give-netanyahu-breathing-room-he-gave-him-an-oxygen-tank/0000018e-372c-d8f9-a98e-7fefdb5d0000</link><description>吉迪恩·萨尔令人费解地退出甘茨的民族团结党，使内塔尼亚胡政府内部反对派的一名关键人物被除名，为总理赢得了宝贵的时间，并可能进一步推迟选举</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/by-leaving-gantz-saar-didnt-give-netanyahu-breathing-room-he-gave-him-an-oxygen-tank/0000018e-372c-d8f9-a98e-7fefdb5d0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷附近发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人受轻伤，嫌疑人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/two-israelis-lightly-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-near-jerusalem-suspect-killed/0000018e-3799-d977-a5ae-7fdd25460000</link><description>17 岁的嫌疑人接近检查站并试图刺伤保安人员，造成一名 25 岁的平民保安人员和一名 19 岁的士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:24:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/two-israelis-lightly-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-near-jerusalem-suspect-killed/0000018e-3799-d977-a5ae-7fdd25460000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长称南非将逮捕持有双重国籍的以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-arrest-israeli-soldiers-holding-dual-citizenship-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-36e3-d0ac-a1cf-3ef7f8650000</link><description>该国外交部长表示，持有以色列和南非双重国籍的以色列国防军士兵将被立即逮捕。以色列军队正在为其他可能效仿的军队做准备</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-arrest-israeli-soldiers-holding-dual-citizenship-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-36e3-d0ac-a1cf-3ef7f8650000</guid></item></channel></rss>